OL,3,CGP surgery rolls out AI scribe tool to
OL,4,Ccut paperwork
OL,6,FGPs in Jersey are now using artificial
OL,7,Fintelligence (AI) to speed up note-
OL,8,Ftaking in routine appointments.
OL,10,FThe Health Plus Practice in St Helier
OL,11,Fis using 'Heidi Health', a form of
OL,12,Ftechnology already used in surgeries
OL,13,Facross 50 other countries, including
OL,14,Fthe UK.
OL,16,FIt allows doctors to focus on
OL,17,Flistening to patients during
OL,18,Fappointments without needing to take
OL,19,Fnotes on a computer at the same time.
