OL,6,FInterim data also suggests that tools
OL,7,Flike 'Heidi Health' are speeding up
OL,8,Fappointments and easing doctors'
OL,9,Fworkload.
OL,11,FLast year's Annual Director of Public
OL,12,FHealth Report highlighted that
OL,13,Fpressure needed to be lowered on
OL,14,FJersey GPs, with the document
OL,15,Fprojecting an extra 43,520
OL,16,Fappointments being needed by 2053.
OL,18,FDigital Jersey has supported the roll-
OL,19,Fout of the AI tool, with CEO Tony
OL,20,FMoretta telling ITV News it is "more
OL,21,Fefficient".
