OL,3,CGP surgery rolls out AI scribe tool to
OL,4,Ccut paperwork
OL,6,FHe explains: "A lot of people want a
OL,7,Fpersonal touch. That's what the GPs
OL,8,Fare there for.
OL,10,F"If the GPs can now focus on the
OL,11,Fpatient - looking at them, examining
OL,12,Fthem, talking to them - then they're
OL,13,Fnot spending their time looking in
OL,14,Ffront of a keyboard, sitting in front
OL,15,Fof a screen.
OL,17,F"There aren't many occasions where you
OL,18,Fhave something that is more efficient
OL,19,Fand has better outcomes, and that's
OL,20,Fthe big advantage of technology, and
OL,21,Fparticularly AI in the health setting."
