OL,6,FWhen asked whether the tool is
OL,7,Fsusceptible to data breaches if it was
OL,8,Fto be hacked, Mr Moretta said the data
OL,9,Fwill "go in the same system that the
OL,10,FGPs will already use and all the GP
OL,11,Fpractices in Jersey use the same
OL,12,Fsystem".
OL,14,FMr Moretta also added that the GP will
OL,15,Fcheck through the notes made by 'Heidi
OL,16,FHealth' to make sure they are
OL,17,Fcorrected, alleviating the risk of
OL,18,Finaccuracies.
