OL,3,CGP surgery rolls out AI scribe tool to
OL,4,Ccut paperwork
OL,6,FHe said: "I would argue that it's more
OL,7,Faccurate that the GP is listening
OL,8,Fcarefully to the patient and in the
OL,9,Ftranscription, there might be an error
OL,10,Fbut these things are really accurate.
OL,12,F"These tools improve all they time and
OL,13,Fthe GP can correct it."
OL,15,FMr Moretta describes the tool as a
OL,16,F"win-win" for doctor and patient,
OL,17,Fadding that the 'Heidi Health' tool
OL,18,Fcan also fill in letter templates to
OL,19,Fspeed up the process of approving
OL,20,Frepeat consultations for patients.
